snippet.title: PLAYGROUND 2 AUCTION | @CarryMinati @triggeredinsaan, Scout, Ashish & Harsh Beniwal
snippet.description:
Playground is back! CarryMinati, Triggered Insaan, Ashish, ScoutOP & Harsh are trying to find the best contestants for the real money auction & pick them for their teams for the season starting 30th January streaming LIVE on YT & on Amazon miniTV! 

Voting lines for Super Subs open on Rumble, closes at 4:30 PM on 30th January. Vote here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.robosoft.playverseStage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Auction rules*
â€¢ 40 contestants
â€¢ Only 28 will remain post auction
â€¢ 20 players, selected through bidding, will go directly into teams 
â€¢ 8 players will go into super subs
 â€¢ Of this, 5 players will be selected by the 5 mentors
 â€¢ And 3 players will be selected through voting on Rumble
â€¢ Player mix for teams - 1 Pro-player, 1 international player, Min. 1 player from previous season, Min. 1 female player
â€¢ Every week two players will get eliminated and new players will be selected from supers subs 
â€¢ 25L purse of each mentor to bid for players

We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 74th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirtiâ€™s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 01 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. Why Vikas Sir's surname is Dvyakirti?
2. What was his UPSC Exam Result?
3. How Dr. Vikas Divyakirti handles Drishti IAS and what is his role?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerabâ€™s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her familyâ€™s decision regarding her and Murtasimâ€™s life. Meerabâ€™s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerabâ€™s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasimâ€™s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3680 - 28 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3680: Taarak's Green Shirt
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal and Taarak make their way to his office. Champaklal becomes unsure about the alibi, which Taarak can inform his boss about. Meanwhile, Taarak's boss video calls him, but he is afraid to answer because he is now wearing a green shirt instead of a yellow one. Champaklal suggests that Taarak make a normal phone call to his boss in order to conceal the truth about the shirt. Everyone in the office is wearing yellow shirts, and Taarak is expected to wear one as well. What happens when he sees Taarak dressed in a green shirt instead? Will Champaklal's cover-up save Taarak? Keep an eye out!

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3679 - 27 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3679: Taarak Phas Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha calls from behind, and Taarak turns around to respond, colliding with a passerby and falling into a mud puddle. As a result, his yellow shirt gets stained. Everyone rushes to Taarak's location. Fortunately, he is not injured, but his shirt is ruined. Taarak blames Jetha for the mishap, but the Gokuldham ladies back him up, claiming that he didn't do it on purpose. Taarak will now wear a green shirt because he was unable to obtain another yellow shirt. Champaklal arrives on the scene and decides to support Taarak in front of his boss. Stay tuned to find out how Champaklal saves Taarak from a reprimand from his boss.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.
